{"tid":964094,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2019戀情第一爆！「EXO」KAI熱戀BLACKPINK成員Jennie","createTime":"2019-01-01T04:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T13:28:43.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aa8f809bd8fcfbc0ea123eb63583a7aa33a60530","tid":964094,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190101/640_bb08490eab918eb644d0b6e70273d658.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190101%2F640_bb08490eab918eb644d0b6e70273d658.jpg&h=d1390954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國媒體《Dispatch》每年都會在1月1日爆出韓星的新戀情，讓粉絲既期待又害怕，而今年的戀情主角正是「EXO」的24歲成員KAI及「BLACKPINK」的22歲成員Jennie，由於2人都是韓國人氣團體的成員，立刻引發網友關注，目前女方所屬經紀公司YG回應，「完全不知道的事，正在確認中」。<br />\n<br />\n《Dispatch》報導，KAI和Jennie從去年10月開始交往，11月25日時曾開自己的BMW，載Jennie到首爾天空公園約會，之後也在自己IG上傳當天天空的照片。而12月2日時KAI結束夏威夷的工作，也開車到Jennie住處送女友禮物。此外今年10月3號KAI與Jennie都在IG曬出巴黎鐵塔的照片，似乎也成了交往證據之一。<br />\nKAI前年4月在愚人節認愛同公司女團f(x)的水晶（Krystal），但在去年6月宣布分手。Jennie則是前後與所屬公司YG的製作人Teddy、甚至是公司老闆楊賢錫傳出戀情，但都遭到否認。（陳明慧／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190101/640_cd50e86fd231d1dd0fb4d1d96d5fcb61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190101%2F640_cd50e86fd231d1dd0fb4d1d96d5fcb61.jpg&h=c8f642ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKAI去年11月25日上傳的照片，被報導指稱是跟Jennie約會時的照片，而此則貼文下方目前也有許多粉絲追問戀情。翻攝KAI IG<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190101/640_aceb86290cbb79958c4b0029e5b6bd4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190101%2F640_aceb86290cbb79958c4b0029e5b6bd4a.jpg&h=bda392bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年10月3號KAI（左）與Jennie都在IG曬出巴黎鐵塔的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20190101/1492844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190101%2F1492844&d=HoBoMebGnLthbdL9qGoKX8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6809a8d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190101%2F1492844&h=8e9406fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20190101/1492844</a>"},{"pid":"c60fa7e5c0414c3e443c91fffc21ab082ac152a2","tid":964094,"uid":120791,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/a3ffa7c47e1c11d54db292faa3ed5a5a/5CA609EE/t51.2885-15/e35/c0.109.872.872/s480x480/45397293_799188157106996_6591798963012276312_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2Fa3ffa7c47e1c11d54db292faa3ed5a5a%2F5CA609EE%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2Fc0.109.872.872%2Fs480x480%2F45397293_799188157106996_6591798963012276312_n.jpg&h=984994c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b309c88fbdd7198c85be00ad42b2d63643c80c10","tid":964094,"uid":55519,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"臭閪"},{"pid":"9da6483afc8fc17d0f59625bc0db60e34df5f5bb","tid":964094,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"而家時下啲明星係咪要改名改到咁標奇立異<br />\n<br />\n叫阿KAI"},{"pid":"444243acc71790e57dc74493402f43d27d280c20","tid":964094,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9da6483afc8fc17d0f59625bc0db60e34df5f5bb","tid":964094,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"而家時下啲明星係咪要改名改到咁標奇立異<br />\n<br />\n叫阿KAI"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"阿佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f921ab4107ce6a68190c3f7f53aa4364eb9e320e","tid":964094,"uid":531,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"目前女方所屬經紀公司YG回應，「完全不知道的事，正在確認中」